### Get customer 100

GET {{baseApiPath}}/customers/100
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get masterdata pdf

GET {{baseApiPath}}/customers/100/generate-pdf?type=MASTERDATA
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get idcard pdf

GET {{baseApiPath}}/customers/100/generate-pdf?type=IDCARD
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get combined pdf

